channel.title: Won't let me download from any mirrors?
channel.description: I have tried all of the mirrors, including the torrent, but after the countdown for the download ends, it wont download. Period. I tried the "If the download does not start automatically, click here." buttons, and they let to broken file downloads. If anyone else has this problem, how can i fix it? Please, and thank you. *EDIT* Also I do have pop-ups unblocked.
